import math
# Define your function here
def SmartSquare(inlist, inplace):
    a = [ ]
    b = len(inlist)
    for i in range(b):
        c = inlist[i]
        d = c ** 2
        a.append(d)
        if inplace:
            inlist[i] = d
            c = d
        else:
            inlist[i] = int(math.sqrt(inlist[i]))
    return a
